TIPPERARY EMIGRANT INDEX : 1828 to 1866

Final update: October, 2011 .

This is the combined index of people who were born in Tipperary , Ireland ,and emigrated to Sydney , New South Wales ,or Moreton Bay , Queensland in the years 1828 to 1866 inclusive . The original form of this index is a SPREADSHEET done in "Microsoft Works". It looks much tidier than this version .

If you would like to do some serious research on it, contact

the author (Peter) on : maddenps(at)westnet.com.au **Change the (at) to the @ symbol and he will send you the original version ,via the internet .

** Make sure you don't have a download limit !

-- because it takes a LOOOONG time for it to bounce !! I only get cranky with people who don't check.

** Please DON'T ask UNLESS you can open MS Works !!

If you wish to be part of it (as a researcher "RSCHR") , send clear details of the persons you are researching to the author at maddenps(at)westnet.com.au **Change the (at) to the @ symbol

Rschr details

will be found at the end of the FAQ page .

To view the list of nearly 300 people who were ALMOST Emigrants , but never actually came ,click on: ALMOST EMIGRANT DATABASE A little research on convicts from Tipperary has been lent to me , and you can view it on : Convict research The "Family Links" page can be found at : Tipperary Family Links The Tipperary Emigrants Death Page can be found at : Convict research A list of thousands of emigrants from Tipperary to Victoria is currently being prepared at : Tipperary Emigrants to Victoria You are very welcome to make contributions to these pages, as the data will need to come from those who HAVE it. Send any details that you'd like to share to Peter at : [email protected] Your contributions WILL be acknowledged. Got any questions about this database ? Check out the "Frequently Asked Questions" Page at FAQ

What's next ??

Whenever useful info comes my way , I'll try to form it into a page that complements this one.
